b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":89,"category_name":"Updates","pr_category_id":"2","title_name":"Update Notification [Addendum]","message":"<div>The update to version 1.1.5 was made available at <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1542164400\\"><\/span>. An automatic update is scheduled to occur at approximately <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1542250800\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>To celebrate the new event, we will be sending everyone a Tenfold Summon Voucher. This announcement will be modified after these vouchers have been distributed.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Version 1.1.5 brings additional features focused on the new event, as well as various improvements and fixes. Check below for details.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Additional features and improvements: [Addendum <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1542173400\\"><\/span>]<\/div><div>The features and changes below have been added to the game.<\/div><div>\\u30fbThe AI of adventurers in your party has been adjusted so that they use attacks and skills more often during quests.<\/div><div>\\u30fbThe Fafnir enemy appearing in the recurring event quest Avenue to Power (Beginner\/Intermediate\/Expert variations) no longer guards.<\/div><div>\\u30fbThe number displaying the amount of eldwater needed to strengthen a co-ability is now easier to see.<\/div><div>\\u30fbFor the upward swiping gesture on iOS devices, it now changes to Multitask during quests after inputting the gesture two times.<\/div><div>\\u30fbDefeated enemies now disappear from the minimap immediately.<\/div><div>\\u30fbThe display speed of Notices has been increased.<\/div><div>\\u30fbThe rates displayed in the item summon&#39;s Appearance Rates have been changed to display up to the thousandths decimal place. The summoning rates themselves are unchanged.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The features and changes below will be added to the game after <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1542261600\\"><\/span>.<br>\\u30fbThe number of skip tickets you can acquire in a Daily Bonus has been increased to three.<br>\\u30fbThe number of skip tickets that you can buy in the shop has been increased to three in one day.<br>\\u30fbThe maximum held number of skip tickets has been increased to 99.<br>\\u30fbAdjustments were made to the power of Hawk&#39;s skill Savage Hawk on stunned enemies.<br>\\u30fbAdjustments were made to Nefaria&#39;s skill Night of Antiquity concerning its power, and power against enemies afflicted with blindness.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Issue fixed:<\/div><div>The following issues have been fixed.<\/div><div>\\u30fbAll of the gifts in the Dragon&#39;s Roost were displaying as bread.<\/div><div>\\u30fbWhile leveling up the Smithy, its level wasn&#39;t being factored into the total Facility Level.<\/div><div>\\u30fbthe High Midgardsorm&#39;s &quot;Storm Chaser&quot; is dealing more hits than it should.[Addendum <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1542174600\\"><\/span>]<\/div><div>\\u30fbChanging characters when one of them has the afflictions stun, freeze, or sleep, then switching back once the affliction has healed, was causing controls to be limited.<\/div><div>\\u30fbFor skills that grow stronger based on the number of buffs on a character, only sustained healing spells weren&#39;t being factored in.<\/div><div>\\u30fbUnder specific conditions, you could be struck by status afflictions while shapeshifted.<\/div><div>\\u30fbWhen choosing to repeat a mission from the quest results screen, the amount of stamina that should have recovered due to passage of time was not being reflected.<\/div><div>\\u30fbFor all of the items on the Friends screen, the might shown on the character that you tap would not reflect the equipped weapon or dragon.<\/div><div>\\u30fbOpening Notices during events would sometimes cause the Notices screen to be displayed lower than the menu, preventing players from pressing the Update or Close buttons.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Notes:<\/div><div>It may take time for the update information to be reflected in the store.<\/div><div>Additionally, users may not be able to perform the update due to their device&#39;s data cache being full.<\/div><div>If you are unable to perform the update, power down your device, then turn it off again and attempt the download from the store after a few minutes.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(41, 105, 176);\\"><strong>To be added <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1542251400\\"><\/span><\/strong><\/span><br>The following will be sent to players who started the game by <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1542250800\\"><\/span>:<br><br>\\u30fbTenfold Summon Voucher x1<br><br>This will be sent to your goodie box when you log in, and you can claim it until <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1542855540\\"><\/span>. This is seven days after it&#39;s sent to your goodie box.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1542166200,"prev_article_id":"58","next_article_id":"111","image_path":"","update_time":1543216034}}}'